HEADWORD: Inexact
<hw>In`ex*act"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> not + <ets>exact</ets>: cf. F. <ets>inexact</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Not exact; not precisely correct or true; inaccurate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Inexactitude</ent>⟦br⟧
